{"tid":503728,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一夜情後被誣告強姦　警協助英女藏匿證據","createTime":"2017-12-19T07:19:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-19T17:21:44.000Z","uid":76115,"like":137,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"ee003518e493b315b0cb68db8362829f1d87c50f","tid":503728,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T07:19:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20171217/1260865/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20171217%2F1260865%2F&d=iD56f6Qx1NMVGz9H89OoLgEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=a1749714\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20171217%2F1260865%2F&h=fe30dcbb\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20171217/1260865/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171217/640_2ae8d9ce4f73f456f23dbc68147ddfbc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171217%2F640_2ae8d9ce4f73f456f23dbc68147ddfbc.jpg&h=54368c92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n艾倫（中）。　翻攝英國《泰晤士報》<br />\n<br />\n英國一名女子不滿性伴侶離她而去，竟誣告他強姦，更離譜的是，警方拒絕交出可以證明男子清白的證據，反「協助」女子一起冤枉他。全案糾纏近2年，男子才被證清白。<br />\n <br />\n22歲的艾倫（Liam Allan）在格林威治大學就讀犯罪學，他被控6項強姦及6項性侵犯罪名，<strong>一旦罪名成立，得入獄至少10年</strong>。法官在周四（14日）還艾倫清白，並要求徹查整個過程。<br />\n <br />\n艾倫表示，過去曾在雙方都同意的前提下，與原告發生一夜情，後來他要上大學，加上對她沒好感，不再與女子見面，對方就誣告他性侵及強姦。<strong>艾倫的代表律師曾要求，調出女子的電話紀錄，以證艾倫清白，不過警方以「對雙方都無好處」為由，拒絕配合</strong>。<br />\n <br />\n艾倫保釋外出近2年，就在開庭前一天，新的檢察官接手本案，要求警方交出女子的電話紀錄，才揭發女子持續騷擾艾倫，又要求艾倫與她做愛。女子又向多名朋友透露，享受與艾倫做愛，甚至坦承有被艾倫強姦的性幻想。<br />\n <br />\n檢察官海斯（Jerry Hayes）表示：「我希望向艾倫道歉&hellip;這可是非常嚴重的司法失誤，可能令艾倫被判非常長期的刑期，及終身列入性罪犯名冊。似乎此案的警員沒有審查證據，這相當駭人聽聞。」<br />\n <br />\n獲還清白的艾倫說：「我無法說清楚，過去2年受到的精神折磨，我相信這個制度會做正確的事，這是我想要加入的制度，但我覺得被這個制度背叛了。」艾倫媽媽則感慨：「在目前的氛圍，在這類案件中，你未被證明是清白前，都被當成是有罪的。」（國際中心／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"c5a8767536ca9130d8a5420c621bdeacdd674a84","tid":503728,"uid":76115,"like":111,"dislike":1,"score":110,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T07:22:23.000Z","msg":"#BelieveAllWomen<br />\n#DontBlameTheVictim"},{"pid":"db374bc00f712472c6a5ebdb0907c5ff1a64a2a4","tid":503728,"uid":30510,"like":60,"dislike":1,"score":59,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T07:26:04.000Z","msg":"#MeToo"},{"pid":"d8a5472b64ef9d64cb9bcfc1fc35a9cfa26cabaf","tid":503728,"uid":131259,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T07:29:37.000Z","msg":"#metoo"},{"pid":"9cbbdd81e899f15b52e42b05b21d4454a2d448b7","tid":503728,"uid":14918,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T07:34:42.000Z","msg":"#metoo"},{"pid":"efa522dad6b0d50d8e2e50e9c48827b1f37f5883","tid":503728,"uid":30370,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T07:34:49.000Z","msg":"告鳩個黑警意圖老防啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d6ec7621f2c9d331f7caf30330ed965c5b8fc2f","tid":503728,"uid":14918,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T09:19:11.000Z","msg":"無人討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee21a5cd9f8428781fbc22301befdab981ddfdc2","tid":503728,"uid":14103,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T09:45:47.000Z","msg":"喂 還左清白 咁隻臭雞同差佬冇手尾跟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"308da112078d6d7e0c77b4a8ef3f7e0a7c8b8eab","tid":503728,"uid":2429,"like":10,"dislike":24,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T09:48:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>喂 還左清白 咁隻臭雞同差佬冇手尾跟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\